0,"quote":{"pid":"457813dc04915db53918a9f5fb6811a2d2fecd86","tid":1834173,"uid":81385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0be78633d959362990286984aa58677dff91e57c","tid":1834173,"uid":37058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"醫護人員要要求支共政府立即閉關 否則即時罷工 為香港人死都無人想見到 何況為支那人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"呢個可以係第5項<br />\n<br />\n由佢地決定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"(肺炎)港府唔限制大陸人來港，我地就令大陸政府限制佢地黎！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1834124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1834124</a><br />\n<br />\n部分患者只有低燒甚至無發燒症狀，邊境測體溫根本唔夠！要既係佢地唔好落黎！<br />\n<br />\nA. 方法：大陸政府最怕大陸人知道既，唔係香港點解抗爭（大陸已經洗曬地，而且大陸人唔care香港人點慘），而係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 高官好有錢（針對仇富心理）<br />\n<br />\n2. 高層全是外國勢力（針對民族主義）<br />\n<br />\n3. 習近平的情人們（針對八掛心理）<br />\n銅鑼灣書店事件係因此書觸怒習而起，雖然本書有點9up，但從事件可見，習真係好驚本書既內容見光<br />\n本書摘要：<a href=\"http://blog.udn.com/meatball2/47616636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Fmeatball2%2F47616636&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=2ed4ec9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/meatball2/47616636</a><br />\n<br />\nB. 形式：<br />\n各大關口、購物熱點（上水、旺角、西九高鐵等）<br />\n連儂牆文宣（各區區議會亦應盡快設定好連儂墻，保障文宣手足安全！）、傳單、街站（大大聲普通話講比大陸人聽）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WAuJnVj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWAuJnVj.gif&h=19f21b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48dBHVk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48dBHVk.gif&h=77b8f461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbQAd10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbQAd10.jpg&h=7af32855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6pk9Ak.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6pk9Ak.gif&h=a6c5bf5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k